The risk of second primary tumors in head and neck cancer: A systematic review.

Coca-Pelaz A(1)(2), Rodrigo JP(1)(2), Suárez C(2), Nixon IJ(3), Mäkitie A(4), 
Sanabria A(5), Quer M(6), Strojan P(7), Bradford CR(8), Kowalski LP(9), Shaha 
