Impact of Combined Lifestyle Factors on All-Cause and Cause-Specific Mortality 
and Life Expectancy in Chinese: The Singapore Chinese Health Study.

Pan XF(1)(2)(3), Li Y(4), Franco OH(5), Yuan JM(6)(7), Pan A(1)(2)(3), Koh 
WP(8)(9).

Author information:
(1)Department of Epidemiology and Biostatistics, School of Public Health, Tongji 
